==English==
===Etymology===
{{F.}} ''résolution''.  {{L.}} ''resolutio'' a loosening, solution.

===Noun===
'''resolution'''

#the state of being [[resolute]]
#(computing) the number of [[pixels]] on the screen
#(hardware) the maximum number of [[pixels]] that can be displayed on a [[monitor]]

